Package: Saqrlab
Title: Simulation and Analysis for Temporal Network Analysis
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Mohammed", "Saqr", email = "saqr@saqr.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simulation tools for temporal network analysis (TNA) research.
    Generates synthetic datasets with known ground-truth parameters for testing
    and validating statistical methods: Markov chain sequences, latent profiles,
    latent classes, regression, factor analysis, and sequence cluster structures.
    All simulation functions return list(data, params) for JSON-serializable
    access to ground-truth parameters.
